<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head> 
	<meta charset="utf-8"/>
	<title>Welcome to Timezones</title>
</head>

<body>
<h2>Thanks for your interest in a Timezones account.</h2>

<p>Please enter your desired password below:</p>
<form method="POST" action="/rsvp-set-password">
